-- Turkey Wants UN’s Chapter 7 Effective on Syria: Minister
-- B y   A l i   B e r a t   M e r i c
-- 2013-09-27T12:04:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-09-27/turkey-wants-un-s-chapter-7-effective-on-syria-minister.html
Chapter 7 allows UN measures to be
enforced by military action or sanctions,  Turkey ’s Foreign
Minister  Ahmet Davutoglu  tells NTV television in interview in
New York.
* Turkey wants to maintain state structure in Syria and
President Bashar al-Assad must not have a place in the new
structure
* Delay in intl action on Syria has caused more deaths
* NOTE: Turkey has volunteered to join any international
coalition to punish the Syrian regime for its alleged use of
chemical weapons on Aug. 21  To contact the reporter on this story:
